## Features ‚ú®

* **Curated Coffee Database:** Explore a hand-picked selection of high-quality coffee beans and roasts.

* **Detailed Information:** Each coffee entry includes tasting notes, origin story, roast level, and recommended brewing methods.

* **Interactive Map:** Discover the best coffee shops near you with an interactive map feature.

* **User Reviews & Ratings:** Share your thoughts and read reviews from other coffee lovers.

* **Brewing Guides:** Step-by-step instructions and tips for various brewing techniques, from pour-over to espresso.

* **Responsive Design:** A seamless experience on any device, from desktop to mobile.

</div>

